      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-all-str-lun        to   w-all-str-i02          .
           subtract  w-all-str-i03        from w-all-str-i02          .
           divide    2                    into w-all-str-i02          .
           add       1                    to   w-all-str-i02          .
           move      w-all-str-wst
                    (1 : w-all-str-i03)   to   w-all-str-alf
                                              (w-all-str-i02:
