      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rn-orf-ndo-num-doc   to   w-att-orf-ndo-nsv      .
           move      rn-orf-ndo-dat-doc   to   w-att-orf-ndo-dsv      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
